query:
WITH moved AS (
            DELETE FROM task WHERE task_id = $1 AND attempt = $3 RETURNING *
        )
        INSERT INTO task_log(
            task_id,
            warehouse_id,
            queue_name,
            task_data,
            status,
            entity_id,
            entity_type,
            message,
            attempt,
            started_at,
            duration,
            progress,
            execution_details,
            attempt_scheduled_for,
            last_heartbeat_at,
            parent_task_id,
            task_created_at
        )
        SELECT task_id,
                warehouse_id,
                queue_name,
                task_data,
                'success',
                entity_id,
                entity_type,
                $2,
                attempt,
                picked_up_at,
                now() - picked_up_at,
                1.0000,
                execution_details,
                scheduled_for,
                last_heartbeat_at,
                parent_task_id,
                created_at
        FROM moved
        ON CONFLICT (task_id, attempt) DO NOTHING
        RETURNING task_id
